{{Infobox rugby league cup | title = Torneo del Nordeste | current_season = | logo = | pixels = | caption = | sport = [[Rugby union]] | founded = 1999 | inaugural = | folded = | teams = 8 | country = {{ARG}} | champion = [[San Patricio Rugby Club]] | season = 2015 | most_champs = [[Taraguy Rugby Club]] (7 titles) | website = | ceo = | TV = | related_comps = }}
The '''Torneo del Nordeste''', commonly known as the '''Torneo del NEA''', is a regional [[rugby union]] competition in [[Argentina]].
The competition started in 1999 and involves clubs from the unions of Union de Rugby del Nordeste (Chaco and Corrientes), [[Union de Rugby de Formosa|Formosa]] and [[Unión de Rugby de Misiones|Misiones]].
As in other inter-provincial tournaments, such as the [[Torneo del Litoral]] or [[Torneo del Noroeste]], the best clubs from the Torneo del Nordeste qualify for the national level [[Torneo del Interior]].
